14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 2401,
16 is amended to read as follows:
17 Section 2401. Sections 4 2401 through 10 2407 of this
18 act title shall be known and may be cited as the "Oklahoma
19 State Regents' Academic Rising Scholars Award Act.".
20 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 2402,
21 is amended to read as follows:
22 Section 2402. A. There is hereby created the Oklahoma
23 State Regents' Academic Rising Scholars Award Program. The
24 purpose of the Oklahoma State Regents' Academic Rising
Req. No. 13243 Page 1
1 Scho lars Award Program is to retain top-ranked students from
2 Oklahoma in Oklahoma colleges, enable Oklahoma institutions
3 of higher education to compete aggressively for top Oklahoma
4 scholars, attract high-caliber out-of-state students to
5 Oklahoma to attend colleges and universities, and enhance the
6 academic quality in Oklahoma colleges and universities. The
7 program shall provide participants funding for enrollment
8 fees, tuition and other fees, room and board and required
9 textbooks or materials for up to five (5) years of
10 undergraduate and/or graduate study at accredited
11 institutions of higher education in Oklahoma.
12 B. The Oklahoma State Regents for Higher Education shall
13 administer the provisions of the Oklahoma State Regents' Academic
14 Rising Scholars Award Program.
